Class PostgresUUIDType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.type.AbstractStandardBasicType<T>
      • org.hibernate.type.AbstractSingleColumnStandardBasicType<UUID>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, BasicType, ProcedureParameterExtractionAware<UUID>, ProcedureParameterNamedBinder, SingleColumnType<UUID>, StringRepresentableType<UUID>, Type

    public class PostgresUUIDType
extends AbstractSingleColumnStandardBasicType<UUID>
    Specialized type mapping for UUID and the Postgres UUID data type (which is mapped as OTHER in its JDBC driver).
